msgid "How to manage organization owners and teams"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../shared/admonition-rtd-business.rst:2
msgid ""
"This feature is only available on `Read the Docs for Business <https://app."
"readthedocs.com/>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:6
msgid ""
"Read the Docs uses teams within an organization to group users and provide "
"permissions to projects. This guide will cover how to manage both "
"organization owners and team members. You can read more about organizations "
"and teams in our :doc:`/commercial/organizations` documentation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:11
msgid "Managing organization owners"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:13
msgid ""
"Organization owners have full administrative access to the organization and "
"all its projects. They can manage settings, teams, members, and other owners."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:17
msgid "Adding an owner to an organization"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:19
msgid ""
"To grant someone full administrative access to your organization, add them "
"as an owner."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:23
msgid "You must be an owner of the organization to add another owner."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-read-the-docs-teams.rst:25
